Title: Tamara
Writer: Andrea Baranenko (story), Fernando Butazzoni (story), Fernando Butazzoni, Joel Novoa (story), Elia K. Schneider (story), Elia K. Schneider
Actors: Luis Fernandez, Prakriti Maduro, Mimi Lazo, Karina Velasquez
Plot: The film is based in the real life of Teo, a distinguished, prominent and outstanding lawyer, with a four year marriage and two small children, who decides to accomplish his long time secret: to change his body and become a woman.
